	<example>
	  <title>
	    Additional packages not delivered with  &company-suse; 
	  </title>
	  <screen>
<![CDATA[
....
<software>
    <extra_packages>
         <package_location>
            custom
         </package_location>
         <packages  config:type="list">
            <package>atftp</package>
         </packages>
    </extra_packages>
    <base>Minimal+X11</base>
</software>
....
]]>
	  </screen>
	</example>
	<para>
	  Using the last example, packages in <emphasis>Minimal+X11</emphasis>
	  will be installed in addition to some extra, user defined packages
	  which will be available in the directory <filename>custom</filename>.
	  </para>